            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR3a0014-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-37a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T23:04:29.564+09:00">韦鼎求见,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-37a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T23:06:16.527+09:00">文中子三次接见他而三次都没有说话,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-37a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T23:06:15.293+09:00">态度却谦恭如有不足。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-37a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T23:04:54.155+09:00">韦鼎出来，对他的学生们说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-37a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T23:05:07.902+09:00">"王老夫子曾经得到过朝廷的器重,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-37a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T23:05:19.076+09:00">所以他不发言而能让人感梧,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-37a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T23:06:00.745+09:00">不发怒而能给人以威严之感。"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-38a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T23:07:07.529+09:00">杨素对先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-38a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T23:07:16.326+09:00">“天子寻求善于守卫边境的人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-38a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T23:07:28.399+09:00">我听说只有贤人才知道贤人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-38a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-02T23:07:37.814+09:00">特向您请教。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-38a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:29:59.702+09:00">先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-38a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:30:12.519+09:00">“羊祜、陆逊</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-38a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:30:17.032+09:00">是仁者，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-38a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:31:38.55+09:00">可以派他们去。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-38a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:31:44.833+09:00">杨素说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-38a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:31:51.614+09:00">“他们都死了，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-38a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:31:55.639+09:00">怎么可以再派他们去呢？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-39a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:33:07.389+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-39a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:33:13.661+09:00">先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-39a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:33:20.204+09:00">“您如果能像羊、陆一样就可以，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-39a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:34:39.88+09:00">如果不能，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-39a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:42:06.135+09:00">四处访求善于守卫边境的人又有什么用呢？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-39a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:42:35.441+09:00">有道是</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-39a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:42:53.545+09:00">‘近者悦，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-39a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:43:08.175+09:00">远者来’，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-39a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:43:19.949+09:00">通过外交手段克敌制胜就可以了，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-39a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T00:45:25.099+09:00">何必要到边境上动武呢？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-40a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T01:21:37.751+09:00">1.30 先生家里</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-40a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T01:13:21.804+09:00">《六经》齐备，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-40a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T01:13:30.43+09:00">朝服和祭器不假借他人。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-40a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T01:13:35.173+09:00">他说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-40a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T01:14:24.139+09:00">“三纲五常自</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-40a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T01:14:46.956+09:00">可由此而出。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-41a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:18:00.325+09:00">1.31　先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-41a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:16:37.075+09:00">“到处都是尸位素餐的人</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-41a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:16:58.888+09:00">王道如何能兴起呢？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-42a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:21:23.788+09:00">西汉的高祖、文帝、武帝、宣帝和东汉的光武帝、明帝、章帝，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-42a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:21:48.569+09:00">他们的人民可以从戎打仗了。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-43a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:35:22.491+09:00">1.33 董常去世，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-43a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:31:14.597+09:00">先生哭于内室门之外，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-43a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:31:30.219+09:00">行叩礼而接受吊唁。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-44a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:36:05.362+09:00">裴晞问：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-44a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:36:18.057+09:00">“卫玠说人有不到之处，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-44a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:36:33.723+09:00">可根据人情加以体谅，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-44a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:37:07.837+09:00">可按照事理而不予追究，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-44a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:37:03.612+09:00">如果不是有意冒犯，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-44a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:37:19.199+09:00">这怎么样？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-44a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:37:29.139+09:00">先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-44a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:37:53.888+09:00">裴晞问：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-44a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:37:42.961+09:00">“算是宽厚了。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-44a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:37:57.11+09:00">“这是不是仁呢？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-44a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:38:41.969+09:00">先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-44a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:38:56.461+09:00">“不知道。” </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-45a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:42:15.09+09:00">裴晞又问：“阮籍和人交谈，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-45a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:42:26.911+09:00">话题玄远，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-45a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:42:41.958+09:00">从不评论他人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-45a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:43:09.485+09:00">这怎么样？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-45a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:43:19.54+09:00">先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-45a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:43:30.71+09:00">“算是谨慎了。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-45a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:43:37.665+09:00">问：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-45a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:43:43.878+09:00">“这是不是仁呢？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-45a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:43:52.723+09:00">先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-45a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:44:56.375+09:00">“不知道。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-46a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:52:27.375+09:00">1.35 先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-46a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:52:47.958+09:00">“凌敬善于体恤人啊！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-46a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T18:53:49.628+09:00">他对待别人的遗孤如同已出。” </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-47a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:48:09.899+09:00">1.36 先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-47a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:16:49.274+09:00">“我见不到仁者，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-47a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:17:52.561+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-47a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:17:55.986+09:00">见到智者</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-47a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:18:00.131+09:00">也行。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-47a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:18:04.175+09:00">我见不到智者，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-47a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:18:28.082+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-47a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:18:32.122+09:00">见到义者</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-47a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:20:20.921+09:00">也行。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-47a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:21:26.268+09:00">如果连这也见不到，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-47a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:21:32.208+09:00">实在不行就刚强和耿介的人吧。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-47a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:21:36.096+09:00">刚强的人能有决断，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-47a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:22:49.876+09:00">耿介的人不同于流俗。” </seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-48a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:49:00.153+09:00">1.37 薛收问何谓至德要道，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-48a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:49:06.484+09:00">先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-48a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:54:55.876+09:00">“至德</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-48a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:54:59.856+09:00">是道的根本吧？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-48a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:55:10.952+09:00">要道</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-48a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:55:19.248+09:00">是德的行用吧？《</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-48a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:55:29+09:00">周礼》不是说了么：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-48a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:55:42.902+09:00">至德为道之本。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-48a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:52:06.747+09:00">《易经》不是说了么：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-48a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T19:52:08.348+09:00">‘显道神德行。’”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-49a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:08:32.842+09:00">1.38　先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-49a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:08:40.723+09:00">“变化之道真是伟大啊！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-49a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:09:52.688+09:00">一切都由此产生。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-49a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:11:11.044+09:00">《易经》真是无以复加了！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-49a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:11:51.508+09:00">它知晓万物变化之道吧？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-50a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:29:45.466+09:00">“我没有见到过好义像好利一样的人。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-51a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:32:43.275+09:00">先生登上云中城楼，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-51a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:32:52.958+09:00">遥望龙门关，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-51a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:33:22.767+09:00">说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-51a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:38:25.971+09:00">“山河牢固，真是雄壮啊！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-51a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:45:09.154+09:00">贾琼说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-51a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:45:24.653+09:00">“山河雄壮之后</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-51a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:46:02.448+09:00">又当如何呢？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-51a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:46:09.147+09:00">先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-51a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:46:19.451+09:00">“用道来守护它。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-51a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:46:32.474+09:00">下来后在禹庙停留，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-51a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:46:39.334+09:00">观看碑首上的文字，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-51a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:46:46.107+09:00">说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-51a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:47:30.385+09:00">文辞雅正而晓畅。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-52a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:58:41.732+09:00">先生看到刘孝标的《绝交论》后</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-52a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:58:47.921+09:00">说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-52a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:58:52.067+09:00">“可惜啊，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-52a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:58:57.935+09:00">称许任昉却诋毁了他。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-52a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:59:25.919+09:00">这样就不能说任昉识人了。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-52a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:59:38.714+09:00">看到《辩命论》后</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-52a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:59:45.652+09:00">说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-52a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-03T23:59:59.295+09:00">“人伦废弃了。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-53a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-04T00:28:42.73+09:00">1.42　先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-53a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-04T00:28:52.178+09:00">“假如诸葛亮不早逝，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-53a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-04T00:29:36.191+09:00">礼乐也许能兴起吧？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-54a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-04T00:45:33.725+09:00">1.43 先生读《乐毅论》，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-54a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-04T00:33:31.572+09:00">说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-54a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-04T00:34:35.78+09:00">“乐毅能有所不为，真是仁爱啊！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-54a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-04T00:37:29.608+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-54a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-04T00:38:21.177+09:00">夏侯玄能发见他的隐衷，真是睿智啊！”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-55a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-04T01:34:38.359+09:00">先生读《无鬼论》，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-55a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-04T01:35:08.069+09:00">说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-55a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-04T01:35:27.507+09:00">“不知道人，卷</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_001-55a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-04T01:35:33.453+09:00">怎么知道鬼？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:16:10.592+09:00">先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:16:13.895+09:00">“圆者动，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:16:18.068+09:00">方者静，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:23:28+09:00">动静往来，这体现了天地的本性啊！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:30:10.734+09:00">先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:32:14.332+09:00">“智者快乐，是因为他成全了外物吧？仁者长寿，是因为他忘怀了自身吧？”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:41:11.462+09:00">楚国公（杨玄感）叛乱，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:41:16.233+09:00">派使者来召请文中子,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:41:22.756+09:00">文中子拒绝前往，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:41:28.763+09:00">对使者说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:41:35.346+09:00">"请代我向楚公道歉。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:41:46.127+09:00">天下战乱之时，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:41:59.455+09:00">只有王公大臣赤血忠诚，天下才能安定。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:42:08.248+09:00">如果不能顺应天时，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-18a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T23:42:46.644+09:00">那么必然是自取祸殃。"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-44a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:27:21.604+09:00">文中子对程元说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-44a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:27:27.645+09:00">"你与董常比怎么样? "</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-44a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:29:12.095+09:00">程元说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-44a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:29:14.027+09:00">"我那里能和董常比,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-44a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:28:36.293+09:00">董常都到了道高忘道、德高忘德的境界，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-44a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:30:12.781+09:00">而我不过是求仁求义罢了。"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-44a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:30:20.482+09:00">文中子说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-44a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:30:29.611+09:00">"董常是这样。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-44a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:30:42.209+09:00">不过你对仁义的追求</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-44a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:31:16.213+09:00">也不很急切,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-44a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:31:28.073+09:00">是否有别的所得?"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-45a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:32:21.831+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-45a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:31:48.219+09:00">董常经常思考，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-45a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:32:10.784+09:00">其余的人只有动静才思考。“</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-45a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:32:26.798+09:00">文中子说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-46a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:46:02.915+09:00">文中子说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-46a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:46:05.579+09:00">"薛收真是够孝的呵！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-46a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:46:09.134+09:00">他父亲被杀，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-47a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:48:03.508+09:00">而他隐遁保全了性命，这既不负于生者也不负于死者。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-47a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-07T01:46:57.279+09:00">文中子当天便去吊祭，终日不笑。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-17a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T21:59:45.815+09:00">贺若弼为炫熠自己高超的箭法,邀请文中子去观看,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-17a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T21:59:52.684+09:00">每发必中。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-17a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T21:59:57.336+09:00">文中子说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-17a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:00:03.726+09:00">"技艺真是精妙啊！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-17a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:00:10.898+09:00">不过，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-17a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:00:14.971+09:00">古代的君子，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-17a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:00:24.015+09:00">一般都致力于大道,以道德为基础，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-17a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:00:35.594+09:00">以仁义为依归,然后才去追求技艺。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-17a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:00:44.995+09:00">贺若弼听后，很不高兴地走了。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-17a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:00:56.471+09:00">为此,文中子对学生们说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-17a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:01:08.947+09:00">"这个人既骄傲又刚愎自用，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-17a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:01:29.652+09:00">在如今的世道立身，恐怕太难了。"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-18a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:19:14.495+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-18a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:19:18.195+09:00">3.16  先生说荀悦：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-18a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:19:28.558+09:00">“这才是史啊！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-18a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:19:42.217+09:00">说陆机：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-18a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:19:47.086+09:00">“这才是文啊！”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-18a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-08T22:45:19.694+09:00">——“他们都近乎道了”。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-19a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:20:03.453+09:00">3.17　先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-19a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:21:03.825+09:00">“文士可由其文章觇见其为人。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-19a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:21:13.448+09:00">谢灵运是小人啊！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-19a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:23:17.54+09:00">他文辞傲慢，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-19a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:23:30.254+09:00">而君子则文辞谨严。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-19a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:23:39.574+09:00">沈约是小人啊！</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-19a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:23:58.215+09:00">他文辞艳丽，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-19a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:24:14.495+09:00">而君子则文辞典重。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-19a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:24:45.771+09:00">鲍照和江淹</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-19a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:24:55.664+09:00">是古代的狷者，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-19a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:25:03.132+09:00">文辞急躁而多怨。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-19a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:25:22.937+09:00">吴均和孔珪</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-19a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:25:31.007+09:00">是古代的狂者，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-19a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:27:13.171+09:00">文辞怪异而忿恚。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-20a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:29:31.892+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-20a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:29:52.723+09:00">谢庄和王融</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-20a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:28:11.369+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-20a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:30:33.015+09:00">文辞琐细。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-20a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:30:39.088+09:00">徐陵和庾信</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-20a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:30:43.34+09:00">是古代的浮夸之人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-20a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:30:49.958+09:00">文辞虚诞。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-20a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:30:53.224+09:00">有人问刘孝绰和刘孝威兄弟，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:31:21.722+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:33:04.015+09:00">“他们是鄙陋之人，文辞放荡。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:33:08.033+09:00">有人问萧绎和萧纲兄弟，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:33:14.045+09:00">先生说：“他们是贪求之人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:33:18.447+09:00">文辞繁缛。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:33:41.162+09:00">又说：“谢朓</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:33:44.581+09:00">是浅薄之人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:33:50.489+09:00">文辞旁逸斜出。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:34:04.836+09:00">江总是</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:34:09.046+09:00">诡诈之人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:34:15.183+09:00">文辞虚妄。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:34:26.543+09:00">他们都是古代的不祥之人。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:34:49.893+09:00">先生说</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:34:59.01+09:00">颜延之、王俭、任昉</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:35:11.191+09:00">“有君子之心，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-21a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T00:35:11.452+09:00">他们的文辞简约而有法则。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-22a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T01:01:11.002+09:00">3.18 尚书召先生出来做官，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-22a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T01:01:15.546+09:00">先生让姚义去替他推辞，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-22a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T01:01:21.82+09:00">说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-22a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T01:01:24.966+09:00">“实在不行，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-22a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T01:01:28.748+09:00">就派我到蜀郡吧。”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-22a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T01:01:48.723+09:00">有人说</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-22a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T01:01:52.224+09:00">蜀地偏远，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-22a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T01:01:56.623+09:00">先生说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-22a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T01:02:23.024+09:00">“我能和严君平、扬雄这些先贤神交往来度过此生，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_003-22a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-09T01:02:50.18+09:00">地方偏僻又有何怕呢？”</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
</TEI>